yTime":"2019-07-28T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"屌你黑警死全家"},{"pid":"bb1642c90d4854185f081e40d60f38ceb3b2958b","tid":1377654,"uid":163957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20eaec825d1cc628486e33e3769b45eba17d2b4e","tid":1377654,"uid":6528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路。<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，但係咁先要做多啲文宣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n做多啲文宣係香港獨立，不過要soft啲可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e6a95f6c952f220cb4bee6f0460fade27ae085","tid":1377654,"uid":260047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aa64c3788f5e39cb3f8de6bcc521fc77cce00eac","tid":1377654,"uid":234831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人渣"},{"pid":"7437542c56c59e5391b22f822583618cf2b45a7f","tid":1377654,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28