方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒做少少文宣係關於香港獨立，不過要soft啲係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1d77dead15cf4a506db22b99bf433684ac4d74","tid":1377654,"uid":103649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"44db4c69cfe46cbcaa7c0f29814d1ae33611fc02","tid":1377654,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024b88302483057425f92b9918f09f69a93cc2bc","tid":1377654,"uid":118350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd7bf952f24d691c1a52dbc5f065e8495dabca11","tid":1377654,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:11:39.000Z","msg":"(728)(TVB)警察使用燃燒彈，並誤中記者！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/angus.lau.963/videos/2083448135094256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fangus.lau.963%2Fvideos%2F2083448135094256%2F&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=7b6795e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/angus.lau.963/videos/2083448135094256/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/lcz2l1cp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Flcz2l1cp&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=e3aedafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/lcz2l1cp</a><br />\n(728)警察特登用盾牌推跌老人家<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alice.ng.0906/videos/10156315649091471/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falice.ng.0906%2Fvideos%2F10156315649